       <br>
      <h5>GENERAL RETURN POLICIES</h5>
      <ul>
      <li>RECEIPTS ARE REQUIRED FOR ALL RETURNS.</li>
      <li>Wolverine Tech and the UVU Store reserve the right to refuse any return of any merchandise that is not in resalable condition.</li>
      <li>All items sold at a clearance price (red price) tag are not returnable.</li>
      </ul>
      <br>
  
      <h5>APPAREL / GIFT / BACKPACK</h5>

       <ul>
      <li>Returns must be made within 7 days of purchase.</li>
      <li>Only items that are unworn, unwashed, and unused, with tags attached, can be exchanged or returned with original sales receipts.</li>
    </ul>
     <br>
  
      <h5>COMPUTERS, TABLETS, APPLE WATCHES</h5>

         <ul>
     <li>A cash register receipt is required for all returns or exchanges.</li>
      <li>Unopened merchandise with factory packaging may be returned for full credit within 7 days of the sale date.</li>
      <li>Configure-to-Order (Custom Computers) are not eligible for returns.</li>
      <li>Opened merchandise will have a 15% restocking fee.</li>
      <li>All returns or exchanges must have all original packaging, be without any cosmetic damage, be able to power on at the time of return, and must be able to perform a factory reset. Any merchandise that cannot meet these conditions will be refused.</li>
      <li>Any product that has been discontinued by the manufacturer is not returnable.</li>
      <li>Wolverine Tech and the UVU Store reserve the right to refuse any return of any merchandise that is not in resalable condition.</li>
    </ul>
    
    <br>
  <h5>DOVER CLASSIC</h5>
             <p>No returns.</p>

      <h5>ELECTRONICS</h5>
 
        <ul>
     <li>A cash register receipt is required for all returns or exchanges.</li>
      <li>Original packaging is required for all returns. Any item that has been opened will have up to a 15% restocking fee depending on the packing condition.</li>
      <li>We do not accept any returns for opened-in-ear earbud headphones.</li>
      <li>We do not accept returns on opened calculators.</li>
      <li>Refunds of electronic items sold one (1) week prior to the refund date need to be approved by Educational Supplies Department personnel.</li>
    </ul>
  
   <br>
   
    <h5>GENERAL READING</h5>
             <p>Returns must be made within 7 days of purchase with the original sales receipt.</p>
             
      <h5>GRADUATION</5>
       <p>Graduation Merchandise is non-returnable.</p> 
       
      <h5>REFERENCE BOOKS, BAR CHARTS, BARGAIN BOOKS</h5>
             <p>No returns.</p>
   
      <h5>SCHOOL / ART SUPPLIES</h5>
   
       <ul>
     <li>Returns must be made within 7 days after purchase with the original sales receipt.</li>
      <li>Merchandise must be in new condition.&nbsp; </li>
      </ul> 
      
